| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-7532 — Recovery Inhibition (ransomhub)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: c7ff21ca-5073-5e29-bf7e-9ab253afa94f"
